#: bluebottle/grant_management/templates/mails/messages/grant_application/activity_manager/application_approved.html:5
#, python-format
msgctxt "platform-email"
msgid "\n"
"Good news, your grant application \"%(title)s\" has been approved!\n"
"<br><br>\n"
"<b>Here’s what happens next:</b>\n"
"<ul>\n"
"    <li>\n"
"        You’ll need to enter your bank details and verify your identity and/or that of the organisation from the grant application page.\n"
"    </li>\n"
"    <li>\n"
"    Once the verification process is completed successfully, the payout will be processed.\n"
"    </li>\n"
"</ul>\n"
"<br>\n"
msgstr "\n"
"Bonne nouvelle, votre demande de subvention \"%(title)s\" a été approuvée !\n"
"<br><br>\n"
"<b>Voici ce qui se passe ensuite :</b>\n"
"<ul>\n"
"    <li>\n"
"        Vous devrez entrer vos coordonnées bancaires et vérifier votre identité et/ou celle de l'organisation depuis la page de demande de subvention.\n"
"    </li>\n"
"    <li>\n"
"    Une fois le processus de vérification terminé avec succès, le paiement sera traité.\n"
"    </li>\n"
"</ul>\n"
"<br>\n"

#: bluebottle/grant_management/templates/mails/messages/grant_application/activity_manager/application_cancelled.html:6
#, python-format
msgctxt "platform-email"
msgid "\n"
"            Unfortunately your grant application “%(title)s” has been cancelled.\n"
"            <br><br>\n"
"            If you have any questions, you can contact the platform manager by replying to this email.\n"
"        "
msgstr "\n"
"            Malheureusement, votre demande de subvention «%(title)s» a été annulée.\n"
"            <br><br>\n"
"            Si vous avez des questions, vous pouvez contacter le gestionnaire de la plateforme en répondant à cet e-mail.\n"
"        "

#: bluebottle/grant_management/templates/mails/messages/grant_application/activity_manager/application_needs_work.html:5
#, python-format
msgctxt "platform-email"
msgid "\n"
"Your grant application \"%(title)s\" has been reviewed and needs work. The platform manager\n"
"will be in contact to help you make some changes to your campaign.\n"
msgstr "\n"
"Votre demande de subvention \"%(title)s\" a été examinée et nécessite des modifications. Le gestionnaire de la plateforme\n"
"sera en contact pour vous aider à apporter des changements à votre campagne.\n"

#: bluebottle/grant_management/templates/mails/messages/grant_application/activity_manager/application_rejected.html:6
#, python-format
msgctxt "platform-email"
msgid "\n"
"            Unfortunately your grant application \"%(title)s\" has been rejected.\n"
"            <br />\n"
"            If you have any questions, you can contact the platform manager at %(contact_email)s.\n"
"        "
msgstr "\n"
"Malheureusement, votre demande de subvention \"%(title)s\" a été rejetée.\n"
"            <br />\n"
"            Si vous avez des questions, vous pouvez contacter le gestionnaire de la plateforme à %(contact_email)s.\n"
"        "

#: bluebottle/grant_management/templates/mails/messages/grant_application/activity_manager/application_submitted.html:5
#, python-format
msgctxt "platform-email"
msgid "\n"
"Your grant application \"%(title)s\" has been submitted on %(site_name)s.<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"<b>Here's what happens next:</b>\n"
"<ul>\n"
"    <li>\n"
"        Your application will be reviewed by the platform manager.\n"
"    </li>\n"
"    <li>\n"
"        Once approved, you’ll need to enter your bank details and complete and complete the verification process.\n"
"    </li>\n"
"</ul>\n"
"<p>\n"
"    You will not be able to edit the application when it is in review.\n"
"</p>\n"
msgstr "\n"
"Votre demande de subvention \"%(title)s\" a été soumise sur %(site_name)s.<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"<b>Voici ce qui se passe ensuite :</b>\n"
"<ul>\n"
"    <li>\n"
"        Votre demande sera examinée par le gestionnaire de la plate-forme.\n"
"    </li>\n"
"    <li>\n"
"        Une fois approuvée, vous devrez entrer vos coordonnées bancaires et compléter le processus de vérification.\n"
"    </li>\n"
"</ul>\n"
"<p>\n"
"    Vous ne pourrez pas modifier la demande lorsqu'elle est en cours d'examen.\n"
"</p>\n"

#: bluebottle/grant_management/templates/mails/messages/grant_application/activity_manager/payout_account_marked_incomplete.html:6
#, python-format
msgctxt "platform-email"
msgid "\n"
"            You are working on a grant application on %(site_name)s.\n"
"            <br/><br/>\n\n"
"            You submitted some information to verify you or an organisations identity, but in some cases we need extra\n"
"            information for a successful verification.\n"
"            <br/></br>\n"
"            Please provide this as soon as possible to avoid issues with your grant application or to resolve them quickly.\n"
"        "
msgstr "\n"
"            Vous travaillez sur une demande de subvention sur %(site_name)s.\n"
"            <br/><br/>\n\n"
"            Vous avez soumis des informations pour vérifier votre identité ou celle d'une organisation, mais dans certains cas, nous avons besoin d'informations supplémentaires pour une vérification réussie.\n"
"            <br/></br>\n"
"            Veuillez fournir cela dès que possible pour éviter des problèmes avec votre demande de subvention ou pour les résoudre rapidement.\n"
"        "

#: bluebottle/grant_management/templates/mails/messages/grant_application/activity_manager/payout_account_rejected.html:6
#, python-format
msgctxt "platform-email"
msgid "\n"
"            You are working on a grant application on %(site_name)s.\n"
"            <br/>\n"
"            <br/>\n"
"            Earlier, you submitted information to verify your identity, but unfortunately, this was not successful.\n"
"            This could be due to various reasons. Please check the link below to make sure your details are correct.\n"
"            If you still have problems, contact the platform manager at %(contact_email)s.\n"
"            <br/>\n"
"            <br/>\n"
"            Please do this as soon as possible to avoid issues with your campaign or to resolve them quickly.\n"
"        "
msgstr "\n"
"            Vous travaillez sur une demande de subvention sur %(site_name)s.\n"
"            <br/>\n"
"            <br/>\n"
"            Plus tôt, vous avez soumis des informations pour vérifier votre identité, mais cela n'a pas fonctionné.\n"
"            Cela pourrait être dû à diverses raisons. Veuillez vérifier le lien ci-dessous pour vous assurer que vos détails sont corrects.\n"
"            Si vous avez toujours des problèmes, contactez le gestionnaire de la plateforme à %(contact_email)s.\n"
"            <br/>\n"
"            <br/>\n"
"            Veuillez le faire dès que possible pour éviter des problèmes avec votre demande ou pour les résoudre rapidement.\n"
"        "

#: bluebottle/grant_management/templates/mails/messages/grant_application/activity_manager/payout_account_verified.html:6
#, python-format
msgctxt "platform-email"
msgid "\n"
"            You are working on a grant application on %(site_name)s.\n"
"            <br/><br/>\n"
"            We have good news! Your identity has been verified, and we will proceed with your application.\n"
"            <br/><br/>\n"
"        "
msgstr "\n"
"            Vous travaillez sur une demande de subvention sur %(site_name)s.\n"
"            <br/><br/>\n"
"            Nous avons de bonnes nouvelles ! Votre identité a été vérifiée, et nous allons poursuivre votre demande.\n"
"            <br/><br/>\n"
"        "

